Naomi asụ nyee nwa iya ono: “Tẹ Ojejoje gọkwaru ọnu-ọma nụ onye ono! Ojejoje, bụ onye ta ahajẹdu okoshi ndu nọ ndzụ mẹ ndu nwụhuwaru anwụhu lẹ ya yeru ẹphe obu.” Yọ sụ Rutu: “Lẹ nwoke ono bẹ ayi l'iya bụkwa mee lanụ; mbụ onye lanụ lẹ ndu ọgbaru oleta ayi ẹnya.”
